\id TIT NT0013.TI1 YAWEYUHA DEIBLERS TFR DP-DEC 21-APR-86 
\h TAETASI 
\toc1 Polokaho Taetasida luhuwa je miye 
\toc2 TAETASI 
\mt1 Polokaho Taetasida luhuwa je miye  
\c 1  
\s1 Taetasida maku meko lo mibo ga.  
\p
\v 1 Nemoya Poloya Omaimidana elekele we ito Jisesi Kalaestikaho aposolo yowanu nimiboya Omaimo dilipe eto ibo wewenasiya monokalalo elewole itae loko ito ga watiya monokau neboya eli wehe litae lokoya yowanu nimibo maya ne.  
\v 2 Yowanunemidana monawaya sakoya ne: Omaiya suwa lokaka amibo welimo hapaya mikaki ito okulumaki soto pamibo onawaloya elewole lepa mutiwa limituwe loko lo mololetoko libokumuya ubolo minoko ewa oko minokaka noune.  
\v 3 Ya gaya Omaimo onawamuya elibo maya kohekaiyoko gala maya li soto nimolayoko le soto molaiye. Omai olisauti lilimekaka welimo gaya wetome okaka yowanuya nemeko lo hukonetaiye.  
\v 4 Monoka anugu ilime molodanaki ilime sa-obo we Taetasiyo, emoki nemokiya makoko monokaya ele elewole oiboma ne. Sao-minoiboma nenako luhuwa maya je noemoyo, elo. Ahote Omai ito We napate Jisesi Kalaestikahoya olisauti lilimekaka wemitokati nasahili ito hulu maya emotoka minadeyo.  
\pi1 \bd 4\bd* 2 Kol 8:23; Gal 2:3; 2 Tim 4:10   
\s1 Kiliti mika owalau Taetasima monoka yowanu leko netibo ga.  
\p
\v 5 Yowanu epawa aha nebo maya le wehe loko le pasetane loko Kiliti mika owalau nohuloetodanaki yowanu ga sa-loko loetoboma ne: Emokahoya muki numuto namatoya moneko monoka we loidawa ujapa we dilipe molatane.  
\v 6 We makolimo lihimala minametibo we, adauti mena makoko lenetibo weya, oluholalesiya eli elewole itabo ito maloka wewenasi emokumu elideko aha nesa-pasalo hulo latila okaka we, hokoliya okaka nesala minametibo, yamidana weya ujapa we dilipe molatane.  
\v 7 Ito Omaimidana yowanulalo ujapa okaka onetibo we netiboya lihimala minametibo minatiye. Sakoya auha lametibo ito enemane oko elewole ga lametibo, ekesa no wavu-leko nametibo, lowa ga lametibo, moni uvaminamu ata keke ametibo minatiye.  
\v 8 Sakokoya wenoka wewena nisideko maya nasahili obetoko dilipe molatibo, ito saina lalomugo umu helitibo, ito you loko netibo, ito wehe loko minoko leko etibo, ito ukau lameda lonetibo, ito upala ujapa oetatibo ne.  
\v 9 Sakokoya lo bebe nouniyoko elewole noibo gaya le ikitoko lenetiye. Yalo jego oko minokaka ga monoka ga laloya lo beko data leko dilipe wehe letiye. Sakokoya lemo monokate liki letikaka niabo wewenasida ganipoya le yeimauka molatiye.  
\v 10 Muki wewenasiya lukaha niae. Sa-ikiki aha gamukiya li yolalo malo iki dokepa jikaka wewena minae. Juda wewenasida ganipomuya dabuha molikaka niabo wewenasiya wavu-liki sa-ikaka niae.  
\v 11 Sa-ikaka niabo wewenasiya moni uvaminamuye liki sihana nesamu api-napi obetatune liki elikiki maloka wesiya menakipasidaya oluhonipolekiya dilipi opa ikaka niabo neyo, yamuya ganunipoya elamilo.  
\v 12 Kiliti mika owalalo minabo wewenasikuti ga monawa ele wehe lonebo we makolimoya sa-loko liye:  
\q1 Kiliti wewenaya edimo suwalo wewena okohimi ulakidana nodenesamu ja ulamo okaka noibomidana lolo ikaka niaboya, aso wewenae liki minadanaki yowanumuya osele delokaka noibo wewena minae.   
\m
\v 13 Sa-ikaka niayoko, nemokahoya aya gamuya eloyoko wehe lone. Sa-oneboya, wavu-leko data leko auha bekaniyoko, eli elewole niabo gaya sino wehe loko minokadeko,  
\v 14 Juda wewenasida hiyega ganipoki aha ganipokiya eli lamikilae. Ito aha wewenasiya Omaimidana gala wehe loko maya demesa mikadanaki aha gaya li hukiminaboya eli lamikilae.  
\v 15 Duka laloki wewenasiya saina-mainamuya elikayoko, ukulo nesagoya lolo noiye. Ito lahelamibo nesalimo dukau siholo kekaiyoko eli elewole amabo wewenasida dukauya siholo kekaiyoko huma jekaka noibo nesa nenako, yamuya edimosiya sainamu elikayoko ayamidana oko siholo keko huma jekaka oko ne.  
\v 16 Edimoya Omaimidana monawalaya ele-minune liki depalotiya likaka niaboya, iki moliki ikaka niabo nesalimo monawanipoya lo soto molokaka noiyoko, wehe lamiye. Aya lahelamabo wewena ga eli hulikaka niabo wewenasiya yowanu laloya litabo aweyaha oko minamiye.  
\pi1 \bd 6-9\bd* 1 Tim 3:2-7   
\c 2  
\s1 Monoka lalomidana ulau ga.  
\p
\v 1 Emoya monoka lalomidana ulautiya wehe loko api-napi oko lo bo.  
\v 2 Sa-loko lo bekadeko, olopa wewenasiya eto iki you liki miniki dupa ujapa iki miniki monoka elitabo nesa ito obohanipo bitabo nesa ito hulu iki miniki asowalaki nesamidana epauya miniki elewole iki minakilae.  
\v 3 Ito ayamidana okogo olopa menakipasida lo bekadeko, monoka menakipa lolo iki aito wewenasida demega lamiki ekesa nomidana elekelelawa minamitae.  
\v 4 Sakiya saina lalomuya api-napi iki li bikadeko, mena owahasiya edimonipo waunipole oluhonipolesitokaya duka moliki ujapa lalo ibitatae.  
\v 5 Ito sa-ikiki olopa menasiya duka ujapa lalo iki dukau ukulo lonedeko miniki numuda ebanipolo miniki saina-mainamu ujapa lalo iki duka laloki miniki waunipolesida maya elekele lalo ibitatae. Sa-ideko maloka wewenasiya mudaidikiki Omaimidana galaya liwi letiwi amitae.  
\v 6 Yamidana oko we owahasida data leko lo bekadeko, dupa ujapa iki eto iki minatae.  
\v 7 Ito saina lalomuya le eto oko uka laloki you loko minoko gahena lo bekolo maya emokahoya anewasuda leko omutokadeko mudaikiki emesaloya molatae.  
\v 8 Monokaya le wehe loko lo bideko, mesaha jamideko monokamu lowa hi limikaka niabo wewenasi lemokumuya lahelametibo ga likili maya ohu jikiki owanipo helikiki hulatae.   
\p
\v 9 Meusa oluho lolo iki aha yowanu liki minikaka niabo wewenasidaya lo bekadeko, we napanipolesida ganipoya eli likiki elekele lalo ibitadeko, we napanipolesiya dumu helitiye. Sakiya we napanipolesida donoto liki edimo ganipoya eli hulamitae.  
\v 10 Sakiya we napanipolesida sainanipohenaya ukele lamiki, ujapa lalo iki yowanu litabo nesalimoya woko wehe lekolaiye. Sa-ikadeko, Omai lilimekaka wemidana monokalaya yamidana mamidana iki li sinatae.   
\p
\v 11 Sa-itabomidana monawaya sakoya ne: Omailimoya numuto namato wewenasidaya olisauti dilimituwe loko aha nesakidana nasahili oletokaka nesaya le soto molaiye.  
\v 12 Sa-okaiyoko, eimola nasahililamoya api-napi olimikoko lilime wehe lokadeko, maya mikauya monoka minamibo aha nesamu lumu helepele okaka udawo nesaya hulikoko lupa ujapa lalo oko wehe loko minoko monokauya Omaimidana owisaloya wehe loko eto oko minakolune.  
\v 13 Sa-udanaki Omai We napate lilimekaka we Jisesi Kalaestida lamedala soto pitibomuya ewa okaka noudawoya onowelaki nesa nenako, yamuya ubolo oko ewa oko minokaka noune.  
\v 14 Emokahoya lemokumuye loko miluma elidanaki, lahelamibo nesa lolo oko minokaka noudawokuti maya lilimituwe loko minoko leko ibolawa maya hulaiye. Sakoko emo wewenala yuha lemodaya lilime eto okadanaki, minoko monoka watiya maya dabuha moliki liki minatae loko nokalawe oletoko lilime wati iye.   
\p
\v 15 Ga maya lo noemoboya le hutili oko lo bitaniyo. Elewole adawomu ele-minoko data leko dilipe wehe letane. Sa-etaniyo, wewena makolimo niseko ilime yeimauka molamideyo.  
\pi1 \bd 14\bd* Sam 130:8; Eks 19:5; Dut 4:20; Dut 7:6; 1 Pit 2:9   
\c 3  
\s1 Wati oko emesalo molatudawo ga.  
\p
\v 1 Emo ujapakalo minabo wewenasida maya akuya esewau leko sa-loko lo bo: Edimoya kiyapenipo ito gamaninipolesida elekele ibitiki yowi-minabo wewenasidaya elekele ibitiki ganipo elitae. Sa-ikiki lalo yowanu aito-aitomidana waitoneboya olo liki litae.  
\v 2 Sakikiya liwi letiwi iki lowa moila hamitae. Sa-ikiki hulu iki miniki muki wewenasida maya dukanipoloti dilipi lahelepa itae.  
\v 3 Hapaya lemotekaho yamidana opa oko nei molokaka nouniyoko, lilimi opa ikaka ae. Sa-okudanaki ga pelesa jeko lelokaka nesamidana elekelewa oetoko minudanaki, wewenasida dilipe opa udanaki, aito wewenasi iki moliki abo nesakidana oko moloko etudawolae lokudanaki, dukau yowe hile hile oko dupamu lelokaka ibo ne. Sakoya sa-minuniyoko, lemodamuya lahelamibo data nikeyoko, edimo depa aha kohalelayoko, lemo lepa aha kohaiduniyoko okaka udawo ne.  
\v 4 Sa-nouniyoko, alika lilime dowa lokaka we Omaimidana nasahilila ito ukala limibo nesa maya soto pekadanaki olisauti lilimiye.  
\v 5 Lemoya wehe loko minoko oko moloko udawo nesa maya watiya neyoko, mudakoko samiye. Ukalaya lemoda lemekoe loko ohatama minoko lekomidana ito noku udokakau Omaimidana weuna oluholokati ohatama soto pekaka nesalimoya lilime dowa liye.  
\v 6 Omailimoya olisauti lilimekaka we Jisesi Kalaestitokati weuna oluhola maya wavu-leko limiye.  
\v 7 Jisesida nasahililamoya Omaimidana omudaloya lilime wehe lokadeko, elewole ebamuya ubolo minokaka noudawo nesa liki sa-itae loko sa-oletaiye.  
\v 8 Aya ga maya watiya wehe loko ne.  
\p Ito maya abuha moloko lo bitane loko noeloe. Sa-okadeko Omaimu eli elewole ikaka niabo wewenasi saina lalo letune likigo yowanu wavu-liki litae. Sa-itabo nesaya lalo nesa nenako, sa-ikadeko muki wewenasidaya dilipe wati etibo ne.  
\v 9 Aya gaya li huli yolalo malo iki minikaka niaboya watiya minamiye, ito ouvamenipoleya hapa yeikalaloka wavu-liki obe-nabe liki mini-liki yowebo ito lowa moila hikaka, ito Mosesekaho lo hukoko libo gamu ligi huligi iki lowa hiwa hiwa ikaka niabo gaya watiya minamibo nenako, ya galoya ele hulikoko emesa mo.  
\v 10 Maloka wewenasiya lahelamibo ga likadeko, luwakuti hiki pou liki mini maloka maloka ikiki maya yu makokohe ito lowe yupekaheya data liki li bitaboya elamideko maya doli hiki hulikadeko, edimonipogo wiki aitoloka minatae.  
\v 11 Ga maya noloboya alo ele-minape. Yamidana ga pelesa jikaka wewenaya madonipo opa ibo minadanaki edimonipo iki moliki abolimo monawanipoya lo soto nomolaiye.   
\s1 Yowanumu loetaidanaki wewena dupamu elaiyoko libo.  
\p
\v 12 Atemasidahe ito Tikikasidahe emotoka doli hekoyoko wikadeko, nemoya Nikopoli numutokaya minatubo neyo, nemotoka nisituwe loko maya abuha molo. Nemoya aya numutokaya lasi okaka yupekaya minatubo nesa lene.  
\v 13 We lowe Apoloki obi ga monawa elekaka ibo we Jenasiyaki edimo monoka yowanulo wisaiye loko nodenesanipoki ito uvaminanipoki le lalo obetatuwe loko abuha molo. Sa-okadeko saina-mainanipomuya ohu jamisaiye.  
\v 14 Wewena yuhatelesiya yowanu lalo li-liki niwiki duka dowa letiye. Sa-okadeko saina lupamidana le wati okakakumuya nasahili yowanu li-liki niwideko, monokau iki moliki itabolimo ihilawa le soto molakolaiye.   
\p
\v 15 Nemoki magoina minudawo wewena mukisiya emo upakamu delokaiyoko noloe. Monokamuye liki duka limikaka niabo wewenasida dupamuya nelokaiyoko noloe. Sa-okaiyoko noloyo, yamuya enemane oko lo bitane.  
\p Ito Omailokati nasahili maya edimotoka mino moloko minadeyo.  
\pi1 \bd 12\bd* Apo 20:4; Ipi 6:21-22; Kol 4:7-8 2 Tim 4:12  
\pi1 \bd 13\bd* Apo 18:24; 1 Kol 16:12   